A room in the Garter Inn.
BARDOLPH
Sir, the Germans desire to have three of yourhorses: the duke himself will be to-morrow atcourt, and they are going to meet him.
Host
What duke should that be comes so secretly?
I hearnot of him in the court.
Let me speak with thegentlemen: they speak English?
BARDOLPH
Ay, sir; I'll call them to you.
Host
They shall have my horses; but I'll make them pay;I'll sauce them: they have had my house a week atcommand; I have turned away my other guests: theymust come off; I'll sauce them.
Come.